  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Antistatic</strong> is a crisp, uncompromising indie platform fighter built in a custom engine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/32bbd22788dcfe9c464690ec001c322d.poster.avif?t=1753306171\" width=338 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/32bbd22788dcfe9c464690ec001c322d.webm?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/32bbd22788dcfe9c464690ec001c322d.mp4?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside a crumbling digital world, atomic combatants carry out their programming in an endless series of battles over the remaining shielded landmarks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local play</strong> — plug in multiple controllers and play together on one screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Traditional mechanics</strong> — shields, directional influence, lag-canceling, grabs, wavedashing, and more </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GameCube adapter support</strong> — natively use the official adapter to play with the most iconic controller for the genre, with a familiar feel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 characters</strong> — all with different play styles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 stage layouts</strong> — some staples, and some new </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/50523eed496e14f45467a0a6c6b022bb.poster.avif?t=1753306171\" width=338 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/50523eed496e14f45467a0a6c6b022bb.webm?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/50523eed496e14f45467a0a6c6b022bb.mp4?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Internationalization Alpha</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rough lookup/machine-assisted language options available for: Spanish, French, Italian, German, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Simplified Chinese, and Traditional Chinese.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/5f599914c9a68bb4c3e0d8d1894144f4.poster.avif?t=1753306171\" width=338 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/5f599914c9a68bb4c3e0d8d1894144f4.webm?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/5f599914c9a68bb4c3e0d8d1894144f4.mp4?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Alpha</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online play is in alpha, but the central matchmaking servers are currently offline. Remote Play Together is the recommended approach for now.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Antistatic</strong> is a crisp, uncompromising indie platform fighter built in a custom engine. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/32bbd22788dcfe9c464690ec001c322d.poster.avif?t=1753306171\" width=338 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/32bbd22788dcfe9c464690ec001c322d.webm?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/32bbd22788dcfe9c464690ec001c322d.mp4?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inside a crumbling digital world, atomic combatants carry out their programming in an endless series of battles over the remaining shielded landmarks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local play</strong> — plug in multiple controllers and play together on one screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Traditional mechanics</strong> — shields, directional influence, lag-canceling, grabs, wavedashing, and more </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GameCube adapter support</strong> — natively use the official adapter to play with the most iconic controller for the genre, with a familiar feel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 characters</strong> — all with different play styles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 stage layouts</strong> — some staples, and some new </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/50523eed496e14f45467a0a6c6b022bb.poster.avif?t=1753306171\" width=338 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/50523eed496e14f45467a0a6c6b022bb.webm?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/50523eed496e14f45467a0a6c6b022bb.mp4?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Internationalization Alpha</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rough lookup/machine-assisted language options available for: Spanish, French, Italian, German, Russian, Japanese, Korean, Simplified Chinese, and Traditional Chinese.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/5f599914c9a68bb4c3e0d8d1894144f4.poster.avif?t=1753306171\" width=338 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/5f599914c9a68bb4c3e0d8d1894144f4.webm?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/944500/extras/5f599914c9a68bb4c3e0d8d1894144f4.mp4?t=1753306171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Online Alpha</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online play is in alpha, but the central matchmaking servers are currently offline. Remote Play Together is the recommended approach for now.</p>",
